OL,6,FThe Chief Executive for the States of
OL,7,FAlderney is no longer in his post.
OL,9,FITV understands that Theo Leijser,
OL,10,Fwho's served as the chief executive
OL,11,Ffor around a year, was gone following
OL,12,Fa behind-closed-doors meeting of the
OL,13,FCommittee for Policy and Finance (P&F)
OL,14,Fon Monday 16 December.
OL,16,FIt comes as the P&F Chair, Nigel
OL,17,FVooght, resigned on Sunday 15 December.
OL,19,FMr Leijser, who was heading Alderney's
OL,20,FCivil Service, was formally accepted
OL,21,Fby Government House on 30 October 2023.
