OL,6,FHowever, his departure now means the
OL,7,Fisland will be looking for its fifth
OL,8,Fchief executive in as many years.
OL,10,FITV News has approached the States of
OL,11,FAlderney's Communication Officer for
OL,12,Fcomment.
OL,14,FHowever, they have also recently
OL,15,Fexited from their post.
OL,17,FInstead, the States refused to confirm
OL,18,For deny who now leads the island's
OL,19,FCivil Service.
