OL,6,FThey stated on Thursday 19 December:
OL,7,F"In response to media and public
OL,8,Fcomment regarding the Chief Clerk the
OL,9,FStates of Alderney in its role as
OL,10,Femployer has the responsibility to
OL,11,Fprotect the data of all of our
OL,12,Femployees.
OL,14,F"Hence matters between an employee and
OL,15,Ftheir employer are for those parties
OL,16,Fonly, and we do not comment on
OL,17,Fspecifics relating to them."
